## Create a new category (admin only)

POST {{baseUrl}}/category
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

{
  "name": "Python",
  "description": "Articles related to Python and AI applications",
  "category_icon": "https://example.com/icon.png",
  "category_image": "https://example.com/image.png"
}

###

## Get all categories

GET {{baseUrl}}/category

###

## Get popular categories

GET {{baseUrl}}/category/popular

###

## Get category by ID

GET {{baseUrl}}/category/2

###

## Get category by slug

GET {{baseUrl}}/category/slug/python

###

## Update a category (full update) (admin only)

PUT {{baseUrl}}/category/2
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

{
  "name": "AI & Machine Learning",
  "description": "Articles related to technology, innovation and digital transformation",
  "category_icon": "https://example.com/icon.png",
  "category_image": null
}

###

## Partially update a category (admin only)

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/category/2
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

{
  "category_image": "https://example.com/new-image.png"
}

###

## Delete a category (admin only)

DELETE {{baseUrl}}/category/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

